author: stefan2
msg: On the fsfs-format7 branch:  Add a function that tests whether a given ID
is an ID with a transaction.  That eliminates the need for users to get
and check the TXN_ID member themselves, i.e. this reduces the dependencies
on the internal representation of said TXN_ID.
This is part of the "numerical IDs" patch series.

author: desruisseaux
msg: Minor change of policy: do not automatically remove whitespaces in Numbers static method;
leave the responsibility to the caller. For such low-level function, it may be preferable
to avoid taking too much initiative.
